{"comments":"TreeView Space-Filling Layout — Treemap and icicle styles.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nSpace-filling layouts use area to represent value. Every pixel of the\ncontainer is allocated to some node, with nested rectangles or bands.\n\n## Algorithms\n\n- Treemap: Nested rectangles, area proportional to value (uses squarify)\n- Icicle: Horizontal bands, one per level\n- Partition: Similar to icicle (alias)\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- TreeView.Types (NodeId)\n- TreeView.Node (Tree, TreeNode, traversal)\n- TreeView.State (ExpandedState)\n- Schema.Graph.Layout (LayoutConfig, TreemapParams)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Layout nodes as nested rectangles (area proportional to value)\n\nUses squarify algorithm for optimal aspect ratios.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Graph","Layout","Config"],"LayoutConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TreeView","Node"],"Tree"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TreeView","State"],"ExpandedState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TreeView","Layout","SpaceFilling"],"LayoutResult"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/TreeView/Layout/SpaceFilling.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"layoutTreemap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Icicle layout (vertical partition)\n\nHierarchical partitions, each level a horizontal band.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Graph","Layout","Config"],"LayoutConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TreeView","Node"],"Tree"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TreeView","State"],"ExpandedState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","TreeView","Layout","SpaceFilling"],"LayoutResult"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[233,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/TreeView/Layout/SpaceFilling.purs","start":[229,1]},"title":"layoutIcicle"}],"name":"Hydrogen.Element.Compound.TreeView.Layout.SpaceFilling","reExports":[]}